{"tid":1544734,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝Lihkg團隊","createTime":"2019-09-05T16:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:17:44.000Z","uid":1003,"like":112,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a62fb9502b975516d084f69cfe6cb623815fd74c","tid":1544734,"uid":1003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"我好少開post<br />\n由高登一路走過嚟<br />\n嚟到依家嘅連登成為今次運動嘅基地<br />\n一個真正屬於香港人嘅討論區<br />\n今日咁大量嘅瀏覽量都無熄過燈<br />\n閂廣告同對應ddos都做得好快<br />\n作為運動基地一定會受中國打壓<br />\n但但你地團隊都一直為香港人做一個屬於香港嘅地方<br />\n多謝LIHKG成個團隊<br />\n希望你地可以一直堅持呢個理念<br />\n正評係畀連仔and his team既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003affbb80634d235e490675c244b46cb3b55c2d","tid":1544734,"uid":257516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"#1003 古老會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2c9584066ac26ca7e4b1eb3ca979394eeb5531","tid":1544734,"uid":51751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連仔 毒撚既驕傲"},{"pid":"8eec9697eeef25ae3615dcc7d6b4618878aaff5d","tid":1544734,"uid":213352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHakqUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHakqUy.jpg&h=947c63be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1456e72191eb9cd24016283e0b338af3e9d79d0f","tid":1544734,"uid":1003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"003affbb80634d235e490675c244b46cb3b55c2d","tid":1544734,"uid":257516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"#1003 古老會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"跟高登過檔過嚟就有咁前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17f9ef908e92191c850e22ed36048e76180e672","tid":1544734,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1944010b5fc51820c232d5c60d8a0e41f4547e12","tid":1544734,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382bfca30caa91b2453b847365236a9858aec1e7","tid":1544734,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"多謝連仔"},{"pid":"7f13333805261760dc732b9dda9f36b4ee17c04f","tid":1544734,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6996ac7b8059b097ce5aa63aaa7a5ae2032f70ac","tid":1544734,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1456e72191eb9cd24016283e0b338af3e9d79d0f","tid":1544734,"uid":1003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"003affbb80634d235e490675c244b46cb3b55c2d","tid":1544734,"uid":257516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2